name: Levi Herbert
subject: These cats
message: Hello, I am a big fan of cats. I want to thank you for the wonderful work that you are doing on raising awareness of cat breeds. This is my favorite site on the internet.

name: Jessica Meowkins
subject: Cat Videos
message: Great site. The cat facts are very informative. I was wondering if it would be possible to add some cat videos or memes to the site. There are a lot of great ones on the internet, and it would be great to have them all organized into one place.
